  "notes": [
    "All lat/lon in decimal degrees WGS84.",
    "decode_centroid is the center of the encoded cell, not the original input.",
    "The centroid_error_m shows quantization: encode then decode does NOT recover the input.",
    "Altitude strings exclude the leading ^; prepend ^ to embed in a full hashsite.",
    "Luhn dots are computed over the FULL string (horizontal + vertical concatenated).",
    "A hashsite with altitude has different dot positions than the same code without altitude."
  ],
